    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained. The exterior paint still holds a great luster, though you will find a few minor stone chips on the hood and small surface scratches near the door handles from normal use. Inside, the cabin is clean and the upholstery is in great shape, showing only light wear on the driver's side bolster. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and has been serviced regularly, making it a dependable choice for anyone looking for a quality pre-owned vehicle that is ready for the road.",
